title: Murphy Homers Again, Mets Sweep Cubs To Reach World Series
text: BING NEWS: Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series CHICAGO (AP) -- One final, charmed swing by Daniel Murphy, and the New York Mets finished a playoff sweep of the Chicago Cubs. A new generation of Amazins is heading to the World Series.
